## §2. 5-axis cross-contribution

- **Q (QUANTUM)**: radioligand binding affinity VQE (peptide-receptor 결합 ΔG); radioisotope conjugate stability quantum-chemical (DOTA-Lu coordination geometry, kinetic inertness); radionuclide decay branching + Auger electron cascade (125I, 111In) cluster-ion DNA damage 시뮬레이션; α-emitter LET (linear energy transfer) ~80 keV/μm vs β ~0.2 keV/μm — high-LET 의 quantum dosimetry.
- **W (WEAVE)**: radioligand chelator scaffold synthesis — DOTA (1,4,7,10-tetraazacyclododecane-1,4,7,10-tetraacetic acid), DOTATATE peptide, PSMA-617 urea-pharmacophore + linker + DOTA; macrocyclic chelator (DOTA, NOTA, DTPA, HBED-CC, SAR-cage) selection per-isotope; bispecific radioligand (PSMA × CD8 etc) W-axis combinatorial.
- **V (VIROCAPSID)**: AAV non-radioactive 직접 fit 없음 — but engineered AAV-NIS (sodium-iodide symporter) gene therapy + 131I theranostic 협업 가능 (oncolytic virus + NIS reporter imaging); minimal direct overlap.
- **RB (RIBOZYME / RNA)**: radioligand RNA imaging research — 18F-labeled antisense oligonucleotide (radio-ASO) for in-vivo RNA imaging; aptamer-radioligand conjugate (RNA aptamer + 177Lu) preclinical paradigm; mRNA-encoded radio-reporter (NIS / HSV-tk) imaging.
- **NB (NANOBOT)**: radioligand nano-delivery — radio-LNP (177Lu-LNP), radio-iron-oxide (radiotheranostic MNP), gold-nanoparticle radio-sensitizer; α-radiosensitizer nano (213Bi-NP) for biofilm/tumor; daughter-isotope retention nano-cage (225Ac → 4 daughter α 추적 retention 문제 → SAR-cage / liposome trap 으로 해결).

