## §4. Phase α–ε — hxq-theranostic-fap-001 candidate

- **Phase α (target select)**: FAP (fibroblast activation protein) — pan-cancer stromal target (FAP+ CAF in pancreatic, gastric, HNSCC, sarcoma); FAP-2286 successor candidate.
- **Phase β (radionuclide select)**: 225Ac α-emitter (high-LET, radioresistant stroma 침투 short-range); back-up 177Lu β for dose-finding.
- **Phase γ (chelator + linker)**: SAR-cage (sarcophagine) for 225Ac daughter retention; PEG12 linker for tumor PK/blood-pool washout.
- **Phase δ (Q-validation)**: VQE FAP-binder ΔG < −10 kcal/mol; DOTA-Ac kinetic inertness Q-simulation t½ >100 h serum.
- **Phase ε (clinical hand-off)**: hxq-theranostic-fap-001 → 225Ac-SAR-FAP successor for pancreatic/gastric/sarcoma post-FAP-2286, leveraging α high-LET on radio-resistant stromal niche.

## §5. raw#10 honest C3 — theranostic paradigm

theranostic 의 historical arc 는 1940s 131I sodium iodide thyroid (Saul Hertz, MGH) 으로 시작 — oldest theranostic, NIS-mediated thyroid uptake + β+γ therapy/imaging. 1994 OctreoScan (111In-octreotide) SSTR2 imaging legacy, 2002 Zevalin (90Y CD20) radioimmunoconjugate 첫 FDA, 2013 Xofigo (223Ra α bone-seeking) mCRPC alpha 첫 approval, 2018 Lutathera (177Lu-DOTATATE) GEP-NET 첫 SSTR2 — NETTER-1 PFS HR 0.21 paradigm. 2022 Pluvicto (177Lu-PSMA-617) mCRPC paradigm shift — VISION trial (NEJM 2021) post-taxane post-ARPI 환자에서 OS HR 0.62 (15.3 vs 11.3 mo), rPFS HR 0.40, FDA 2022.03 승인 → PSMA radioligand 가 mCRPC 의 새로운 표준 치료 진입. 2023-2024 expansion: pre-taxane setting (PSMAfore Phase 3) 적응증 확대, FAP-2286 pan-cancer (Novartis ex-Clovis 2024 acquisition), Clarity Pharma SAR-bisPSMA 64Cu/67Cu pair, POINT PNT2002 SPLASH Phase 3. **Pluvicto 의의**: SSTR2 (희귀 NET) 너머 PSMA (대규모 mCRPC ~200,000명/년 미국) 가 첫 large-population radioligand market 으로 — radioligand 가 niche 에서 main-stream oncology 로 도약. **alpha emitter (225Ac) next-gen**: 225Ac-PSMA-617 Phase 3 진입, 177Lu-resistant 환자 + radioresistant niche 에서 high-LET 효과; 211At (cyclotron-produced), 213Bi (225Ac generator), 212Pb (224Ra generator) α 가 차세대 — but supply scarcity 가 bottleneck. **FAP-2286 pan-cancer expansion**: FAP+ CAF (cancer-associated fibroblast) 가 pancreatic/gastric/HNSCC/sarcoma 공통 stromal target → pan-cancer radioligand 가능성 (PSMA-mCRPC, SSTR2-NET 다음 큰 indication 확장). **한국 K-radioligand**: 한국 핵의학회 (KSNM) 강력 + 식약처 (MFDS) 임상 진입 — 서울대, 삼성의료원, 분당서울대 PSMA radioligand 한국인 임상 진행, 듀켐바이오 / 퓨쳐켐 / 라디오디 등 한국 radiopharma 회사 부상; 국내 cyclotron (서울대, 가천길 등) 18F/68Ga 생산 + 한국원자력연구원 (KAERI) 99Mo/177Lu/225Ac 생산 노력. **양자-VQE 의 radioligand binding fit**: peptide-receptor 결합 (DOTATATE-SSTR2, PSMA-617-PSMA, FAP-2286-FAP) 은 small-medium 분자 + 단백질 pocket interaction → VQE 정밀 계산 적합 영역; chelator-radiometal coordination geometry (DOTA-Lu, SAR-Ac) 도 quantum-chemical 정확 fit. **chelator stability fit**: kinetic inertness (in-vivo demetalation 방지) 가 radioligand 안전성의 결정적 요소 — DOTA-177Lu 안정 수일, DOTA-225Ac 는 daughter (221Fr, 217At, 213Bi, 209Pb) recoil 으로 chelator 탈출 → daughter retention 문제 → SAR-cage / liposome / NP 격리 (NB-axis) 솔루션. **supply chain challenges**: 225Ac global production <2 Ci/year (Oak Ridge ORNL Th-229 source + Russia + Germany) → actinium scarcity; 177Lu reactor (러시아 ROSATOM, ITM 독일, NRG 네덜란드) 의존; 68Ga generator + 18F cyclotron 은 분산 가능; cyclotron-producible α (211At, 225Ac via 226Ra) scale-up 진행. **future direction**: (a) α-emitter 확대 (225Ac, 211At, 212Pb) high-LET radioresistance 극복; (b) Auger-emitter (111In, 125I, 67Ga) 핵-targeted nano-scale DNA damage; (c) bispecific radioligand (PSMA × CD8, FAP × HER2) cooperativity; (d) pretargeting (TCO/Tz click-chemistry in-vivo) 로 PK 분리; (e) combination radioligand + DDR inhibitor (PARPi, ATRi) 시너지; (f) personalized dosimetry (image-based, K-radioligand 한국 강점); (g) radio-PROTAC (radio-degrader hybrid) cross-platform 융합.

